GT

   GT is the grouptell command. You use this command to tell your group 
something. The group members do not have to be in the same room to hear
a grouptell.

ex. gt I had to flee guys, ill be back in a sec.

/* somewhat bug infested.  group leader may not hear gt's from members */
/* may not be able to gt to people who are outside the zone or in */
/* other rooms.  Testing and debugging required -Batopr */

